sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 로그인 회원
    participant JS as detail.jsp fetch
    participant RC as CommunityReactionController
    participant RS as CommunityReactionServiceImpl
    participant RM as CommunityReactionMapper
    participant PM as CommunityPostMapper
    participant DB as Oracle

    User->>JS: 좋아요 클릭
    JS->>RC: POST /community/like/toggle
    RC->>RS: toggleLike(postId, member)
    RS->>RM: countLikeByPostAndMember
    RM->>DB: SELECT TB_POST_LIKE
    alt 이미 좋아요
        RS->>RM: deleteLike decreaseLikeCnt
    else 미좋아요
        RS->>RM: insertLike increaseLikeCnt
    end
    RS->>PM: selectPostDetail likeCnt
    RC-->>JS: JSON liked likeCnt
    JS->>JS: 버튼 숫자 갱신
